---
import Icon from '@/shared/components/Icon.astro'
---

<section class='solution' id='solution'>
  <div class='wrapper'>
    <div class='solution-header' data-aos='fade-up'>
      <span class='solution-label'>La solución</span>
      <h2 class='solution-title'>
        Vende más rápido, <span>trabaja menos.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class='solution-subtitle'>
        Gadmin Webs convierte tu catálogo en una experiencia de compra rápida, profesional y
        directamente conectada a tu WhatsApp.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class='solution-cards'>
      <div class='solution-card' data-aos='fade-up' data-aos-delay='100'>
        <div class='solution-card-icon-wrap'>
          <div class='solution-card-icon'><Icon name='bolt' size={32} /></div>
        </div>
        <h3 class='solution-card-title'>Carga Instantánea</h3>
        <p class='solution-card-text'>
          Tu catálogo vuela, tus clientes no esperan. Cero PDFs pesados, cero esperas. Una
          experiencia rápida que <strong>convierte visitantes en compradores.</strong>
        </p>
        <div class='solution-card-tag'>+300% más rápido que un PDF</div>
      </div>

      <div class='solution-card solution-card--featured' data-aos='fade-up' data-aos-delay='200'>
        <div class='solution-card-badge' style='display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;'>
          <Icon name='star' solid size={14} /> Estrella
        </div>
        <div class='solution-card-icon-wrap'>
          <div class='solution-card-icon'><Icon name='shopping-cart' size={32} /></div>
        </div>
        <h3 class='solution-card-title'>Carrito Directo a WhatsApp</h3>
        <p class='solution-card-text'>
          El cliente elige productos, arma su pedido y te lo envía <strong
            >organizado y completo</strong
          >
          por WhatsApp. Tú solo despachas.
        </p>
        <div class='solution-card-tag'>Pedidos sin errores</div>
      </div>

      <div class='solution-card' data-aos='fade-up' data-aos-delay='300'>
        <div class='solution-card-icon-wrap'>
          <div class='solution-card-icon'><Icon name='code-bracket' size={32} /></div>
        </div>
        <h3 class='solution-card-title'>Sin Conocimientos Técnicos</h3>
        <p class='solution-card-text'>
          Nosotros nos encargamos de que todo funcione. Tú solo vendes.
          <strong>Cero código, cero complicaciones.</strong>
        </p>
        <div class='solution-card-tag'>100% gestionado por Gadmin</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .solution {
    padding: 6rem 1rem;
    background: var(--shade-03);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .solution::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(77, 93, 239, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    filter: blur(80px);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .solution-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 3.5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .solution-label {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.25);
    color: #22c55e;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .solution-title {
    font-size: var(--48-pt);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--white);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .solution-title span {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #22c55e);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .solution-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .solution-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 72rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .solution-card {
    position: relative;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 1.25rem;
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem 2rem;
    transition:
      transform 0.3s ease,
      box-shadow 0.3s ease,
      border-color 0.3s ease;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .solution-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    border-color: rgba(77, 93, 239, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(77, 93, 239, 0.12);
  }

  .solution-card--featured {
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(77, 93, 239, 0.1) 0%, rgba(20, 238, 244, 0.05) 100%);
    border-color: rgba(77, 93, 239, 0.2);
  }

  .solution-card-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    right: 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .solution-card-icon-wrap {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: rgba(77, 93, 239, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(77, 93, 239, 0.15);
  }

  .solution-card-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    display: flex;
  }

  .solution-card-title {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .solution-card-text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 400;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .solution-card-text strong {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
  }

  .solution-card-tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.35rem 0.85rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2);
    color: #4ade80;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 1024px) {
    .solution-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 500px;
    }

    .solution-card--featured {
      order: -1;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .solution {
      padding: 4rem 1rem;
    }

    .solution-title {
      font-size: var(--40-pt);
    }

    .solution-card {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
